Usage instructions:

 1) Download vision from http://vision.shopify.com
 2) Unpack vision in a folder of your choice
 3) Unpack this theme to the vision directorie's themes folder
    
    Example
    
      vision/
      vision/server
      vision/themes
      vision/themes/turtles.myshopify.com   <- PLACE HERE
      vision/vision.rb
      [...]
      

 4) Start Vision with the appropriate executable for your platform and edit away!